videos.headline: Washington scores on their first drive
videos.description: Jake Browning pass complete to Dante Pettis for 3 yds for a TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington scores on their first drive) 2016/09/30

videos.headline: Gaskin muscles through for another Huskies touchdown
videos.description: Washington running back Myles Gaskin's second effort gets him into the end zone, giving the Huskies a 13-0 lead over Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gaskin muscles through for another Huskies’ touchdown) 2016/09/30

videos.headline: Huskies open up 23-0 lead on Cardinal
videos.description: Jake Browning fires his second touchdown of the game finding John Ross for a 19-yard score to extend Washington's lead to 23-0 over Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Huskies open up 23-0 lead on Cardinal) 2016/09/30

videos.headline: Washington recovers fumble off of Stanford players' back
videos.description: Tristan Vizcaino punt for 35 yds , Ben Edwards returns for no gain to the Stanf 40 Ben Edwards fumbled, recovered by Wash Lavon Coleman

videos.headline: Gaskin scores second TD to continue beat down over Stanford
videos.description: Myles Gaskin runs in for his second touchdown, this time from eight yards out, to increase Washington's lead to 30-0 over Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gaskin scores second TD to continue beat down over Stanford) 2016/09/30

videos.headline: Washington forces Stanford turnover in red zone
videos.description: Ryan Burns sacked by Psalm Wooching for a loss of 4 yards to the Wash 12 Ryan Burns fumbled, forced by Psalm Wooching, recovered by Wash Keishawn Bierria

videos.headline: R. Burns pass to J. Arcega-Whiteside for 19 yds for a TD
videos.description: Ryan Burns pass complete to JJ Arcega-Whiteside for 19 yds for a TD

videos.headline: The rout goes on for Washington
videos.description: Jake Browning throws his third touchdown of the game, this one to Aaron Fuller, to raise Washington's lead to 37-6 over Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (The rout goes on for Washington) 2016/09/30

videos.headline: Coleman breaks free for TD
videos.description: Lavon Coleman runs for the 25-yd touchdown that puts Washington up 46-6 on Stanford.

videos.headline: Washington takes next step with rout of Stanford
videos.description: Washington coach Chris Peterson joins SVP to break down the Huskies improving to 5-0 after a 44-6 rout of Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Washington coach Chris Peterson after Stanford win) 2016/9/30 SVP SC
